        <title type="html"><![CDATA[[TCP]service-model]]></title>
        <id>https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/[TCP]service-model</id>
        <link href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/[TCP]service-model"/>
        <updated>2024-05-24T03:22:09.806Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[向 Application Layer 提供的服务 Socket API]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>向 <code>Application Layer</code> 提供的服务 <code>Socket API</code></p>
</blockquote>
<table><thead><tr><th>Property</th><th>Behavior</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Stream of bytes</td><td>Reliable byte dilivery service</td></tr><tr><td>Reliable delivery</td><td>1. Acknowledgements indicate correct dilivery</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>2. Checksums detect corrupted data</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>3. Sequence numbers detect missing data</td></tr><tr><td></td><td>4. Flow-control prevents overruning receiver</td></tr><tr><td>In-sequence</td><td>Data delivered to application in sequence transmitted</td></tr><tr><td>Congestion Control</td><td>Controls network congestion</td></tr></tbody></table>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_qb_P" id="reliable-delivery">Reliable delivery<a href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/[TCP]service-model#reliable-delivery" class="hash-link" aria-label="Reliable delivery的直接链接" title="Reliable delivery的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<ol>
<li>保证传输</li>
<li>保证内容</li>
<li>保证无丢失</li>
<li>保证在缓冲范围内接受</li>
</ol>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_qb_P" id="tcp-segement">TCP Segement<a href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/[TCP]service-model#tcp-segement" class="hash-link" aria-label="TCP Segement的直接链接" title="TCP Segement的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>两个 <code>Stream</code> 之间的同步</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_qb_P" id="tcp-segment-flags">TCP Segment Flags<a href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/[TCP]service-model#tcp-segment-flags" class="hash-link" aria-label="TCP Segment Flags的直接链接" title="TCP Segment Flags的直接链接">​</a></h3>
<ol>
<li><code>SYN</code>: 发送同步信号</li>
<li><code>ACK</code>: 确认序列号有效</li>
<li><code>FIN</code>: 连接的一端关闭</li>
<li><code>PSH</code>: 连接的另一端立即传送数据</li>
</ol>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_qb_P" id="socket">Socket<a href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/[TCP]service-model#socket" class="hash-link" aria-label="Socket的直接链接" title="Socket的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>使用 传输层编程提供的 <code>Socket API</code> 实现自定义应用层的功能，可以使用 <code>TCP</code> 提供的服务</p>
</blockquote>]]></content>
        <category label="network" term="network"/>
    </entry>
