        <title type="html"><![CDATA[link-layer]]></title>
        <id>https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/link-layer</id>
        <link href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/link-layer"/>
        <updated>2024-05-24T03:22:09.806Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[Address Resolution Protocol ARP]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_qb_P" id="address-resolution-protocol-arp">Address Resolution Protocol <code>ARP</code><a href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/link-layer#address-resolution-protocol-arp" class="hash-link" aria-label="address-resolution-protocol-arp的直接链接" title="address-resolution-protocol-arp的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>from <code>IP Address</code> to <code>MAC Address</code></p>
</blockquote>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_qb_P" id="dns-vs-arp"><code>DNS</code> vs. <code>ARP</code><a href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/link-layer#dns-vs-arp" class="hash-link" aria-label="dns-vs-arp的直接链接" title="dns-vs-arp的直接链接">​</a></h3>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_qb_P" id="arp-table"><code>ARP</code> Table<a href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/link-layer#arp-table" class="hash-link" aria-label="arp-table的直接链接" title="arp-table的直接链接">​</a></h3>
<ol>
<li>广播形式查询 <code>ARP</code>，链路层帧形式响应 <code>ARP</code></li>
<li><code>ARP Table</code> 是即插即用的，不需要维护，过了 <code>TTL</code> 之后，就会被清除</li>
</ol>
<blockquote>
<p>TTL 通常是 20 分钟</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_qb_P" id="以太网协议">以太网协议<a href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/link-layer#%E4%BB%A5%E5%A4%AA%E7%BD%91%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE" class="hash-link" aria-label="以太网协议的直接链接" title="以太网协议的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_qb_P" id="ethernet-card-interface-网卡">Ethernet Card (Interface) (网卡)<a href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/link-layer#ethernet-card-interface-%E7%BD%91%E5%8D%A1" class="hash-link" aria-label="Ethernet Card (Interface) (网卡)的直接链接" title="Ethernet Card (Interface) (网卡)的直接链接">​</a></h3>
<blockquote>
<p>6 字节，16 进制表示</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 class="anchor anchorWithStickyNavbar_qb_P" id="链路层地址-mac-address">链路层地址 <code>MAC Address</code><a href="https://zhuqiandai.github.io/confucianism/blog/link-layer#%E9%93%BE%E8%B7%AF%E5%B1%82%E5%9C%B0%E5%9D%80-mac-address" class="hash-link" aria-label="链路层地址-mac-address的直接链接" title="链路层地址-mac-address的直接链接">​</a></h2>
<blockquote>
<p>NOTES: 主机和路由器并没有链路层地址，适配器 (<code>Interface</code>) 具有链路层地址</p>
</blockquote>]]></content>
